title: Ep. - 314 - JENNA LYONS FROM STYLISH WITH JENNA LYONS ON HBO MAX DOUG BUDIN TAKES A FOOD NETWORK RECIPE TEST STEVE STAUFF RECOMMENDS LIFETIME MOVIES
description:
Designer Jenna Lyons, Chief of Staff Kyle DeFord and Creative Director Sarah Clary of HBO Max’s Stylish with Jenna Lyons, which follows Jenna and her team of designers as they tackle design projects ranging from home renovations to launching new fashion brands.

 

Doug Budin is tested on his ability to decipher what is a real or fake recipe by The Pioneer Woman, Ree Drummond.

 

Steve Stauff gives a guide to Lifetime Movies this holiday.
